


Secrets have new line at the end 
===============

echo "password" | tr -d \\n | base64 -w 0

===============
Fixes the issues

********* Sample shell ********
#!/bin/sh


echo "Input : $1"
echo " ****** Encoded ******"
echo -n "$1" |  base64
echo "\n===================="
echo " ****** Decoded ******"
echo "$1" | base64 -d
echo ""



Disable opentracing Jaeger
  OPENTRACING_JAEGER_ENABLED: "false"
